2. Get some perspective - Limit social media time (ini kayaknya paling ngaruh di jaman sosmed kayak sekarang) - Think of everything you’ve every accomplished in those 30 years - Encourage you to find examples of people who are not old and boring.
Beberapa cara biar bisa survive: 1. You are not alone *tenaang ternyata banyak temen senasip sepenanggungan yg merasakan hal sama

"Panicking because every single person around you (literally, every one of them) has all of this stuff figured out and you are the only one who doesn’t" --> ini sih efek rumput tetangga terlihat lebih hijau aja kayaknya, tp emang cukup berpengaruh sih. Berasa butiran debu
